  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Supply Wigs to Needy Michigan Children</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Wigs 4 Kids reaches out to kids and young adults with hair loss by providing custom-fitted, age-appropriate wigs, indivudally cut and styled for that child at no cost to the kids or their families. This program is available to any Michigan child or teen through age 18 experiencing hair loss due to cancer treatments or various other appearance related challenges that cause hair loss such as: alopecia, trichotillomania, lupus, hydrocephalus, burns and other disorders.</narrative>
  </description>
